The welp proceeded to get bigger and cause me pain to where I couldn?t use my arm in less than a week. Before I knew it, it was the size of a golf ball in my right arm. The doctor denied that the cause for my symptoms would have anything to do with that. But yet the doctor said I was fine and nothing was wrong and sent me away within a few hours.
